'''List of Shikinai Shrines in Shima Province''' (志摩国の式内社一覧) is a list of {{ill|Shinto shrine|de|Shinto shrine|ja|神社|zh|Shinto shrine|qq=draft}} recorded in Volumes 9 and 10 "Kaminachō Jōge" of the {{ill|Engishiki|de|Engishiki|ja|Engishiki|zh|Engishiki|qq=draft}} ({{ill|Engishiki Jinmyōchō|1=Engishiki Jinmyōchō|2=ja|3=延喜式神名帳|4=zh|5=延喜式神名帳|6=simple|7=Engishiki Jinmyōchō|1=Engishiki Jinmyōchō|2=ja|3=延喜式神名帳|4=zh|5=延喜式神名帳|6=simple|7=Engishiki Jinmyocho|de|Engishiki Jinmyōchō|1=Engishiki Jinmyōchō|2=ja|3=延喜式神名帳|4=zh|5=延喜式神名帳|6=simple|7=Engishiki Jinmyōchō|1=Engishiki Jinmyōchō|2=ja|3=延喜式神名帳|4=zh|5=延喜式神名帳|6=simple|7=Engishiki Jinmyocho|ja|延喜式神名帳|1=Engishiki Jinmyōchō|1=Engishiki Jinmyōchō|2=ja|3=延喜式神名帳|4=zh|5=延喜式神名帳|6=simple|7=Engishiki Jinmyōchō|1=Engishiki Jinmyōchō|2=ja|3=延喜式神名帳|4=zh|5=延喜式神名帳|6=simple|7=Engishiki Jinmyocho|zh|Engishiki Jinmyōchō|qq=draft}}) that are known as {{ill|Shikinai Shrine|de|Shikinai Shrine|ja|式内社|1=Shikinaisha|2=ja|3=式内社|qq=draft|1=Shikinaisha|zh|Shikinai Shrine|qq=draft}} and their {{ill|candidate shrines|de|candidate shrines|ja|論社|zh|candidate shrines|qq=draft}}, and are classified under the {{ill|Shima Province|de|Shima Province|ja|志摩国|zh|Shima Province|qq=draft}}.

